## 🎯 Project Objective & ADF Alignment

This project builds the investigation and response skills a RAAF Cyber Warfare Officer needs when an incident occurs on defended systems. The role requires the ability to rapidly acquire evidence, analyse it, reconstruct attacker actions, and recommend containment and recovery steps. By simulating a real compromise from my earlier pentest, I practised the full forensic workflow in a controlled environment.

